---
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-medium text-slate-900 mb-6">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">
          How long until I see results?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
          <p>Most clients see movement in their Google Maps ranking within the first 30-45 days. Organic search rankings typically take 3-6 months to fully mature depending on your market and competition.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">
          Do I need to spend money on ads?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
          <p>No. Our entire system is built around organic visibility. We get you traffic that you don't have to pay for every time someone clicks.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">
          What if I'm already with another SEO company?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6-6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
          <p>We can seamlessly take over your existing campaigns. We'll run an audit to see what they've done, keep the good parts, and fix the rest. Many of our clients come to us after being burned by generic agencies.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">
          Is there a lock-in contract?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
          <p>We require an initial 3-month commitment because SEO takes time to build momentum. After that, it's completely month-to-month. We keep our clients by delivering results, not with legal documents.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">
          What exactly do I get for $500/month?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
          <p>You get our full 3-pillar system: Complete Google Maps management, ongoing website SEO for Page 1 rankings, and our automated 5-star review engine. It's everything you need to dominate local search.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <details class="group bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">
          How is this different from other SEO companies?
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-600">
          <p>Most agencies do a little bit of everything for everyone. We only do local SEO for service businesses. We know exactly what works for tradies and local services, and we don't waste time on vanity metrics — we focus on getting your phone to ring.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
